# Supabase Security

- Use Row Level Security.
- Use private storage rules for sensitive files.
- Student card images are private to the owner and admin only.
- Vendor cannot see student verification documents.
- Phone numbers are private until an approved consent request.
- Vendor cannot see student phone unless approved.
- Vendor can manage only own shop, menu, posts, and related vendor data.
- Chat messages are visible only to conversation participants and admin where moderation requires it.
- Never place service role keys in the mobile app.

